Sentencas: La0.6Sr1.4MnO4 (LSWO4) layered perovskite with K2NiF4 structure was prepared and evaluated as anode material for La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3-delta (LSGM) electrolyte supported intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: La0.6Sr1.4MnO4 layered perovskite anode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction results show that LSMO4 is redox stability.
Titulo: La0.6Sr1.4MnO4 layered perovskite anode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thermal expansion coefficient of LSMO4 is close to that of LSGM electrolyte.
Titulo: La0.6Sr1.4MnO4 layered perovskite anode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
